  <brief_title>Mechanisms and Factors Responsible for the Inhibition of Transposons During Fetal Gonad Development in Humans</brief_title>
  <official_title>Mechanisms and Factors Responsible for the Inhibition of Transposons During Fetal Gonad Development in Humans</official_title>
